'''Stink-beetles''' were [[Yuuzhan Vong]] creatures. To be compared to one was an insult. During the [[Terraforming/Legends|worldshaping]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], the [[World Brain]] accidentally overbred them, then due to another accident, killed them off, resulting in a pelting rain of dead stink beetles from the sky.

